original: Jansson, Janne Herman, rektor, Kalmar, f. 6/10/07 i V. Sönnarslöv, Krist. 1. G. 39 m. Helene Ohlsson. Barn: Bengt Olle f. 40, Lars Göran 43. — Folks.k:lär:ex. i Lund 29. Folk-sk :lär. i V. Karups skoildistr. 30, Malmö stads skyddshem 31-37, Ö. Spångs skolhem 38-45, rektor v. Gudmunds-gårdens skolhem i Kalmar sed. 45.
translated: Jansson, Janne Herman, principal, Kalmar, b. 10/6/1907 in V. Sönnarslöv, Krist. 1. Married in 1939 to Helene Ohlsson. Children: Bengt Olle b. 1940, Lars Göran b. 1943. - Completed teacher training program in Lund in 1929. Worked as a teacher in V. Karup's school district in 1930, Malmö city residential home from 1931-1937, Ö. Spång's school home from 1938-1945, became principal at Gudmundsgården's school home in Kalmar since 1945.
